<BlogPost
  title="Prompt engineering for business: stop writing better prompts, start building better systems"
  description="Most prompt engineering advice misses the point for business use. Individual prompts don't scale. Here's how to move from prompt tweaking to building systems that deliver consistent results without you in the loop."
